Description: A BLOOD PH TEST IS A NORMAL PART OF A BLOOD GAS TEST OR ARTERIAL BLOOD GAS (ABG) TEST. IT MEASURES HOW MUCH OXYGEN AND CARBON DIOXIDE ARE IN YOUR BLOOD
THE PARTIAL PRESSURE OF CARBON DIOXIDE FROM ARTERIAL BLOOD (MM HG). RANGES 35 TO 45 MMHG, OR 4.7 TO 6.0 KPA.
OXYGEN SATURATION FROM ARTERIAL BLOOD (%) SAO2
